<meta property="og:title" content="Space" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Space
Marilyn Buck
              [This poem is read by Akwasi Evans.]
Today I would like to be in space
free-floating
not in a damned no-space
space ship
I already live in a no-space
place
a 5:00 bus
feet in the aisle
we careen off
each other
bang into beds
Aii yee!
I need som" />
<meta property="og:type" content="article" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://freedomarchives.org/wild-poppies-the-poems/space/" />
<meta property="og:site_name" content="Freedom Archives" />
<meta property="article:publisher" content="https://www.facebook.com/freedomarchives" />
<meta name="twitter:title" content="Space" />
<meta name="twitter:description" content="Space
Marilyn Buck
              [This poem is read by Akwasi Evans.]
Today I would like to be in space
free-floating
not in a damned no-space
space ship
I already live in a no-space
place
a 5:00 bus
feet in the aisle
we careen off
each other
bang into beds
Aii yee!
I need som" />
