<div class="container container-normal">
    <div class="row maincontent lower">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
                 
        <div class="post"> 
            <div class="entry">
                <h4 style="padding-left: 30px;">Space</h4>
<h5 style="padding-left: 30px;">Marilyn Buck</h5>
<p class="center" style="padding-left: 30px;">              [This poem is read by <a href="https://freedomarchives.org/contributors-to-the-wild-poppies-album/">Akwasi Evans</a>.]</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Today I would like to be in space<br />
free-floating<br />
not in a damned no-space<br />
space ship<br />
I already live in a no-space<br />
place<br />
a 5:00 bus<br />
feet in the aisle</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">we careen off<br />
each other<br />
bang into beds</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Aii yee!</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">I need some space!</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">nothing personal<br />
but my person<br />
is drifting<br />
trying to get away<br />
from this space<br />
to breathe and swim<br />
in the deep green pool<br />
of my imagination<br />
bubbles wait<br />
to break the surface<br />
in a dizzy explosion<br />
into galaxies<br />
and the universe</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">                                   July 1995</p>
<h5 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://freedomarchives.org/publications/wild-poppies-a-poetry-jam-across-prison-walls-2/">About the CD</a> | <a href="https://freedomarchives.org/wild-poppies-the-poems/">The Poems</a> | <a href="https://freedomarchives.org/contributors-to-the-wild-poppies-album/">The Contributors</a> | <a href="https://freedomarchives.org/about-marilyn-buck/">About Marilyn Buck</a></h5>
<p><a class="btn get-copy" href="https://co.clickandpledge.com/advanced/default.aspx?wid=33028">Get A Copy</a></p>
<p style="text-align: right;">poems © the authors<br />
compilation © <a href="http://www.freedomarchives.org/index.html">The Freedom Archives</a></p>
                
                             </div>
        </div>
         


 
